Charm is an offensive spell, so they will be mad at the one charming him.<br>
<br>
You probably need a puller to get Rottgrime alone.<br>
When he is alone, then both a chanter and a necro can charm him, but a healer might be a good thing, because a few charms can be resisted or interrupted.<br>
All chanter charms from 49 and up can be used, but tashing before charming is adviced.<br>
I think the 49 necro charms and up can be used too.<br>
<br>
When he is charmed you can turn in the braid.<br>
Expect to turn in many braids to see faction changes.<br>
One quest handin seems to give around 3 faction hits, at max 5.<br>
If you are max KOS, then you should expect to do the quest MANY times, according to the post in this thread.<br>
